title: Damn Fine Cast Conversation
itunes:title: Damn Fine Cast Conversation
description:
Episode 196 - It's another podcast mashup! I speak to Scott and Tony of the amazing soundtrack focused podcast, Damn Fine Cast (a reference to Twin Peaks for those interested in the name). We discuss the beauty of podcasting, introductory soundtracks and the connection of punk/hardcore to this world. It's a great time and I hope that you enjoy!This weeks show is brought to you by Audible!
